---
title: Remodeling Blog
meta_description: >-
  Practical remodeling advice for Bozeman homeowners — bathroom costs, basement
  finishing, deck building, and what to expect when you remodel.
h1: The Plane Truth
hero_image: /img/hero/plane-truth-header.webp
hero_subtitle: 'Insights, Opinions, and Rants - from a Remodeler''s Point of View'
permalink: /blog/
layout: layouts/page-simple.njk
---


<div class="blog-grid">
{% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
  <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="card blog-card">
    {% if post.data.featured_image %}
    <img src="{{ post.data.featured_image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
    {% endif %}
    <div class="blog-card-body">
      <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      <p class="blog-card-meta">{{ post.date | dateReadable }}</p>
      {% if post.data.meta_description %}
      <p class="blog-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.meta_description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </a>
{% endfor %}
</div>
